						               													<description>Seven Deadly Sins can be best describe as a New Age Snake-and-Ladders with Attitude. The board comprises a winding &amp;amp; overlapping path divided into seven different incarnations -Killer, then Thief, Liar, Servant, Lover, Healer, and finally Prophet. Players must race from Creation to Nirvana through the incarnations while collecting money, Mojo, cards and other elements along the way. Some cards, Wicca Cards, can be used to cast spells so as to advance yourself or to retard the progress of others, other cards provide protection. To win you must be first to reach Nirvana with at least 50 units of Mojo.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Takes around 20 mins per player (therefore 3 player games take approximately 60 mins).  Some of the content is too much for young children, thus the game's 13+ rating.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
